Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞 瑪麗亞在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易達阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燉小腿肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心多做了呢 就想分給你些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 這是怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是嬰兒的撥浪鼓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰給的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威利 過來幫我搬東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…個 少爺的內褲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中 上次的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 萬事都按少爺的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做好在那裏住宿的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 少爺 我們去哪旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連那種事都不知道還來捆行李嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個執事 解約
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王殿下應該是在大約在三天前到達了巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在視察萬博會的會場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必酒店的警戒應該很嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心不在這裏對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下要挑起歐洲的…不…世界的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是去覲見女王的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為那個叫阿巴萊恩特的人的死感到悲傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個棋子無視了我的命令 煩人地幹涉進來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把握住棋子的意圖和戰力的話 是玩不成遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從埃菲爾塔入場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰神廣場的會場裏美術宮和各個展覽館林立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從鐵道運來的大量的貨物 凝聚了藝術的精華的機械展館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特羅卡迪羅廣場是農業展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第二會場榮軍院廣場裏正在舉行殖民地博覽會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其內容為古代遺跡的重建 民族工業 人類 動物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與往年不同的是從美國來的牛仔的野性秀還有失常工業之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的萬博會 也為了新商品的開發 再稍微四處轉轉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 驚奇宮裏好像有天使的標本出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是值得一看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的標本？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽啊 只不過是猴子而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中生存下來的您的話 這點程度的黑暗根本不算什麽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺請去會場外面避難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中奔跑一點也不難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的靈魂一直在黑暗中奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏真的是我生活的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這麽慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾 好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在新世紀之前 將歐洲改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏在溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏在沈澱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏有汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有將全部破壞一次的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不破壞就沒有創造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了迎接潔凈的新世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國將吹起席卷一切的風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法多姆海恩府是我凈化的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麽的惡趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…這裏\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫敦大橋正在倒下來 倒下來 倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫敦大橋正在倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我美麗的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓您告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽不僅僅是殺掉 還要制造出那麽悲慘的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能將危險放置一旁不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾 那是凈化哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕蔑死者是您所謂的凈化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輕蔑了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕蔑 我… 對一直以來對我盡忠的法多姆海恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少能一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您吃驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像是散發著年輕氣息的少女一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下在幸福的半途中失去了心愛的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下哀傷著夫君的死 曾一度也想了解自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為了能與心愛的夫君一起永遠的一起生活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將陛下的身體與夫君的身體連在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫君理解我做出的行動 並對此感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣夫君的身體就…怦怦地在跳著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怦怦 生命的躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與相愛的人一起成為真實的意義那種喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想贈與法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其死決不會成為淒慘之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麽想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下與夫君擁有將英國指引向純凈的強烈的意誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其誌向將自己的汙穢一掃而光 成為了這樣純潔的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麽崇高的誌向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與月下的天使正相配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞修 至少讓夏爾在你的刀刃下終結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞修的刀刃是非常美麗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直像沐浴在新世紀的朝日光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對著智慧的榮耀拔出劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你體內的野獸拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把他推進深淵裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你有純白色的來世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾·法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是自己擅長的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊不中的話也是沒有意義的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這就是終點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 請下令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將亞修…殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅有這些…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將女王…殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麽荒唐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這個東西停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 只會增加騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是普通的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽要在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就此撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽讓我停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引人註目 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望是對讓自己落入地獄的人復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那日的誓言是怎麽說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您將我喚醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事實永遠不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經付出的代價永遠不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將成為您的劍 幫您完成復仇的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其代價為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂什麽的 不論多少都讓你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那日的您應該沒有猶豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了事實 還要向女王盡忠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從一開始就沒有對她的忠誠心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是作為法多姆海恩家的主人行動罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 靈魂真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂什麽的怎麽可能有 真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了驛館後 請好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人討厭的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始 取掉了我的襯衫的紐扣的你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過讓惡魔來模仿執事的工作 你還做的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為法多姆海恩家的執事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話就到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該休息了 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忘記一切 願您有個幸福的美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有再一次獲得未來的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍棄女王的看門狗這一稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍棄一直懷抱的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯…蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯蒂安 去哪了 早上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯蒂安！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是702室的法多姆海恩 隨從去哪了知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印記沒有消失 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忘記一切 願您有個幸福的美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家夥才不會希望我有什麽幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 「忘記一切」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訣別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到倫敦之類的事 我自己一人也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我帶到加萊的港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 小子 那是拜托別人的態度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說去是加萊的港口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思呢 不巧我家是反方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布洛涅港口的話 就往反方向一直走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 慢慢地拐來拐去的話 遲早會到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你這家夥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出和我給你的代價相應的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一晚 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了倫敦再補寄給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麽玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是誰嗎 夏爾·法多姆海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪的小販
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道法多姆海恩公司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個指環 是法多姆海恩代代相傳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽就這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那個指環做代價就讓你住下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺不錯的石頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐也給你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麽玩笑 區區一個便宜旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 來這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵 連你也耍本少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麽近的地方…有港口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣我也 那樣仿徨著 沒有找到它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明…在如此近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水…去拿水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
