*Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在奔跑
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊燃燒的倫敦
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在奔跑
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麽
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在奔跑
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了用能讓家夥認同的靈魂來迎來終結
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 那個執事 起火
*Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是個執事…的主人罷了
